<h4>Welcome to Darts Checkout Assistant</h4>
<p>You can use this site to lookup a checkout while you=E2=80=99re playing,=
 learn different ways to take out a number, or find great practice routines=
 to help you improve your dart game.</p>
<p>As we move forward, we=E2=80=99ll cover the basics of playing the =E2=80=
=9901 games, discuss dart strategy, and analyze various checkouts. Follow u=
s on Twitter to stay up to date.</p>
